::Cygnar::
    "I suppose an optimist would say things are still getting better.  After 
all you gained a command, the group will regrow, I am now in a position to 
aid in the confrontation, and the rest will return someday."  He glances 
around the room and lowers his voice.  "And we will soon be able to defeat 
the Trainers.  This battle is not just for the safety of our base.  It has 
much higher stakes.  If we can take them out, we will gain the reputation of 
ferocity our faction deserves.  We must meet with the Predacon commanders 
again.  Now that the rampaging bot has been stopped we must plan a battle.  
For the moment we will have to work with the Predacons in all of our battles. 
 We don't have enough bots to mount an effective attack."
